title: [Twisted Trail]
description: A gust of moisture-heavy wind buffets you, nearly knocking you off the ledge you stand on.  Set back on the rock shelf is what appears to be a ruined temple.  The remnants of colored glass hang in the windows, and the doorway is empty.  A warped and faded wooden sign lies on the ground before the building, set at an odd angle that suggests it was ripped from the face of the structure.

A gust of moisture-heavy wind buffets you, nearly knocking you off the ledge you stand on.  Set back on the rock shelf is what appears to be a ruined temple.  The remnants of colored glass hang in the windows, visible only during the fitful flashes of lightning, and the doorway is empty.  A warped and faded wooden sign lies on the ground before the building, set at an odd angle that suggests it was ripped from the face of the structure.
